<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>About Us - Adventure Campers</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/about-us.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <header>
      <h1>Welcome to Adventure Campers!</h1>
      <p>Your gateway to unforgettable camping adventures.</p>
    </header>

    <main>
      <section id="about">
        <h2>About Us</h2>
        <p>
          At <strong>Adventure Campers</strong>, we are passionate about
          bringing people closer to nature. Founded in 2015, our mission has
          been to create unforgettable camping experiences for individuals,
          families, and groups. Whether you're a seasoned adventurer or new to
          the outdoors, we have something for everyone!
        </p>
      </section>

      <section id="mission">
        <h2>Our Mission</h2>
        <p>
          Our mission is to inspire a love for the great outdoors while
          promoting sustainable camping practices. We aim to create meaningful
          connections between people and nature through well-organized trips
          that focus on safety, fun, and environmental responsibility.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section id="services">
        <h2>What We Offer</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Guided camping trips for all skill levels</li>
          <li>
            Customizable group packages for families, schools, or corporate
            events
          </li>
          <li>Survival skills training and workshops</li>
          <li>Eco-friendly camping equipment rentals</li>
          <li>Destination camping at breathtaking locations</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section id="testimonials">
        <h2>What Our Customers Say</h2>
        <blockquote>
          "Adventure Campers provided the best camping experience I've ever had.
          The guides were knowledgeable, and the trip was both fun and safe.
          Can't wait for my next adventure!" – <em>Sarah W.</em>
        </blockquote>
        <blockquote>
          "Our corporate retreat was a huge success thanks to Adventure Campers.
          The team-building activities were fantastic!" – <em>John D.</em>
        </blockquote>
      </section>
    </main>

